approved: true
description: <p>Marck Script is based on freehand \
  lettering with felt-tip pen by Marck Fogel. The \
  main advantage over other similar fonts is the \
  lack of connections between characters, that \
  allows wide variety of spacing between letters. \
  It can be used for logotypes, headlines and for \
  short pieces of text, wherever you want to \
  create an informal, confident relationship - \
  it is readable, comfortable and welcoming.</p>

font.MarckScript-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

font.MarckScript-Regular.ttf.style: normal

